{"tid":1727722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分化警隊，由交通警開始","createTime":"2019-11-16T14:06:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T17:26:36.000Z","uid":76382,"like":455,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"b5be6c5ccc043d9f37858165fc089188f8e0406a","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:06:49.000Z","msg":"是咁的，今日搭巴士返屋企，<br />\n發覺條街多咗好多車泊雙黃線，甚至有Double Parking問題<br />\n諗起尋日睇過脫髮巴打出過兩個post<br />\n（最新職業：錄音師　<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1723358/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1723358/page/1</a><br />\n新職業：電話師<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1722900/page/1）\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1722900/page/1）</a><br />\n於是我就有少少愚見想分享下<br />\n方法都係不外乎扮對話、自言自語，目標／對象一樣都係港豬、藍絲、（偽）中立派<br />\n有幾個方向俾大家討論下：<br />\n<br />\n1. 普通過馬路市民<br />\n例：屌班交通警都垃撚圾嘅，啲防暴啊速龍啊就日日對付班暴徒，屌你老味班交通警連指揮交通都懶，岩岩個老人家喺紅綠燈企咗幾分鐘先過到馬路啊！<br />\n2. 司機（職業／假日／普通司機皆可）<br />\n例：屌吖班暴徒打爛哂十字路口啲燈，岩岩架大車唔收油隊埋嚟，差啲就冇命啦！啲交通警除咗識開槍仲識乜嘢？<br />\n3. Dobule Parking / 泊黃線 車主<br />\n例：&quot;喂XXXXX好難搵泊位架喎&quot; &quot;屌驚閪咩，依家啲交通警都唔做嘢架啦，你有見過佢地出嚟做嘢咩？<br />\n4.  Dobule Parking / 泊黃線 受害者<br />\n例：班交通警都唔知死撚哂去邊，依家XXXX日日都double parking，搞到成日塞死哂！<br />\n5. 飛車黨 受害者（呢個假啲）<br />\n例：依家班飛車黨肆無忌憚，晚晚喺度響喉嘈住哂，都唔知啲交通警死哂去邊！<br />\n<br />\n希望慢慢啲人會開始諗，係喎好似真係睇咁耐新聞都唔覺交通警有做嘢（剩係識開槍）<br />\n然後再適當地褒獎防暴速龍，拉一派打一派，班交通警一定會更加嬲<br />\n甚至班日日食TG又要驚俾人私了嘅狗都會開始諗到底交通警點解可以彷彿置身事外咁 <br />\n到時佢地內部一內訌，就可以製造更多分化對立<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMon Post Sir 請廣傳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4076e7644d02a2f0b02df3b786f2958495b26c31","tid":1727722,"uid":137900,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:07:25.000Z","msg":"Pull"},{"pid":"b374ce066ed9159a39081e98d25f568fc5aedf5c","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:08:36.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d49c80d38444ce67a9a8db4876e9dbace75d58d","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:08:48.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e24474a1568668de65326909d9299a758cea4f95","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:08:59.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4591887c63532faee83d0ebdd376947bd4ddade5","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"317c7815f9d79725d12ba5353089106a748b756a","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:37.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d2aab324f58c489091f660caa9e8b8421d27b7","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:48.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d219bdba4de3ad398c0a21ff1db87defaac0777c","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:09:58.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e095e2eaef8ccff0e69ffa2ea2ac3fde25ac9767","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:43.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"220add7c1f749741e793598213a8fa89a5fe68fc","tid":1727722,"uid":76382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"認同請分享 <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma